<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>125</hymn_number>
<aka>Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli hokʋt</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli hokʋto,
 Ʋba yakni achukma,
 Pim aiasha ikbi hocha,
 Ʋba yoka ia tok.

[V2]
 Yʋmohmi ka okla momʋt
 Iloh ia pullashke;
 Nana achukma fehna ka
 Pim atahli tok oke.

[V3]
 Hatak yoshoba chia ma!
 Hina hanta foyukʋt,
 Chisʋs a binili hoka
 Eho pesa pullashke.

[V4]
 Okla cho moma hokʋt
 Himak a fehna hoka,
 Chisʋs atihi̱ya tok a̱
 Eho foka pullashke.</lyrics>
<title>Exhortation to follow Jesus. ƲIT125</title>
<time_sig>8.7.8.7.</time_sig>
</song>